- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): Matrix completion is also a common problem in image and video processing, which falls under the scope of computer vision. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The proposed model can be used for collaborative filtering, which is a common technique in information retrieval. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper proposes a generic method for joint training of the factorization model and the discretization operator, which involves algorithmic techniques.
